  "description": "Designed to couple with Olvido — the tape mechanism feeds the spectral erosion engine like two forms of forgetting working in parallel. Three heads across a 4-second reel let the bias drift under LFO control, creating slow wavering that Olvido's f\u00b2-scaled decay reads as organic memory loss. Open high-pass space above 8kHz keeps the coupling channel clean.",
